you
will,
there
is
but
one
object
in
the
room,
and
that
the
most
sinister,
to
which
Matthew's
face
seems
to
bear
an
affinity,
and
of
which,
ever
and
anon,
it
reminds
you
strangely
the
eruption
of
Vesuvius?
Flame
and
shadow
seem
the
component
parts
of
that
lad's
soul
no
daylight
in
