"Concede,
conciliate,"
is
their
motto
wherever
he
is
concerned.
The
republicans
are
fast
making
a
tyrant
of
their
own
flesh
and
blood.
This
the
younger
scions
know
and
feel,
and
at
heart
they
all
rebel
against
the
